title: Be A Man S01E01 - Association - HD MP4.mp4
description:
<a href="http://www.copactionvideo.com/" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW">http://www.copactionvideo.com/</a>

Made to assist the Victorian police force, this helpful video explains to young, impressionable officers that "corruption" is "bad". Victoria Police Chief Commissioner Ken Lay made his own video about this: http://media.theage.com.au/news/national-news/ken-lays-message-to-police-over-corruption-4143476.html

We at Cop Action Video think our version is a bit "edgier".

Interestingly, this is also the first, teaser, episode of 2014's most exciting animated cop show, BE A MAN! Eight more episodes to come.
